= SDL_DestroyTexture =
Use this function to destroy the specified texture.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_DestroyTexture(SDL_Texture* texture)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''texture'''
|the texture to destroy
|}

